verbose_text: In NSPC cultures, where the direct effects of GC can be more easily interpreted [XREF_BIBR], CORT and the specific GR agonist DEX inhibited NSPC proliferation, leaving a 20% of cells unaffected, in agreement with the relative abundance of GR-NSPC in the cultures.
evidence: CORT and the specific GR agonist DEX inhibited NSPC proliferation
